ount lookup. No PDA persistence change needed. vrf_request_key added to event. |\n    83→| FR-7.6 rematch | Creates new open match | Player clicks \"Play Again\" → new match with same tier/side. Opponent must find and join from lobby — no forced rematch. |\n    84→| FR-6.5 estimated wait time | Still deferred | Requires match fill-rate analytics infrastructure that doesn't exist. |\n    85→| FR-8 audio | Deferred to dedicated audio spec | All 4 audio items out of scope for this pass. |\n    86→| Carry-forward items | Included as validation checklist item | One combined validation item covers all 5 pivot carry-forward checks. |\n    87→\n    88→## Notes\n    89→\n    90→- Source material (COINFLIP.md) is well-specified for core flows\n    91→- All blocking items resolved during /refine interview (2026-02-17)\n    92→- 12 granular checklist items in spec, ordered by dependency\n    93→- 8 functional requirements extracted, all with acceptance criteria\n    94→- Validation plan covers all critical paths\n    95→- Phase 2 refinement (2026-02-26): 14 new checklist items for gap closure after 004 rewrite\n    96→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a3554eb9-5d3e-4470-b8e4-3c2e723bd989","uuid":"9b26f4f7-dcdb-4f4e-9084-24cb7d4490d8","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/checklist.md","content":"# Specification Quality Checklist: 001 Coinflip\n\n**Purpose**: Validate specification completeness and quality before implementation\n**Created**: 2026-02-12\n**Refined**: 2026-02-17\n**Spec**: [spec.md](spec.md)\n\n---\n\n## Content Quality\n\n- [x] No implementation details (languages, frameworks, APIs)\n- [x] Focused on user value and business needs\n- [x] Written for non-technical stakeholders\n- [x] All mandatory sections completed\n\n## Requirement Completeness\n\n- [x] No [NEEDS CLARIFICATION] markers remain\n- [x] Requirements are testable and unambiguous\n- [x] Success criteria are measurable\n- [x] Succe