{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01TbhdCgzNp4v4QZi1jtNd48","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XTJXzzdgqqQs9ofoUipq4C","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/gap-analysis.md","content":"# Gap Analysis: 001-coinflip — Coinflip\n\n- **Date**: 2026-02-26\n- **Spec status**: Done\n- **Previous analysis**: 2026-02-18 (pre-004 rewrite)\n\n## Implementation Inventory\n\n### On-Chain Instructions\n\n| Instruction | Program | File | Line |\n|------------|---------|------|------|\n| initialize_config | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/initialize_config.rs | 24 |\n| create_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/create_match.rs | 28 |\n| join_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/join_match.rs | 25 |\n| claim_payout | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs | 55 |\n| cancel_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/cancel_match.rs | 24 |\n| timeout_cancel | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs | 32 |\n| force_close | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/force_close.rs | — |\n| initialize_platform | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/initialize_platform.rs | 25 |\n| create_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/create_player_profile.rs | 24 |\n| update_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/update_player_profile.rs | 20 |\n\n**Architecture**: 3-tx flow — create → join(+Orao VRF request) → claim(+VRF read + settle). The previous `resolve_match` instruction was deleted in the 004 shared-infrastructure rewrite; resolution is now handled at claim time by reading Orao VRF randomness on-chain.\n\n### Shared Crate\n\n| Export | Module | File | Line |\n|--------|--------|------|------|\n| SIDE_HEADS / SIDE_TAILS | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 2-3 |\n| PHASE_WAITING / LOCKED / SETTLED / CANCELLED | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 6-9 |\n| LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS (120) | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 12 |\n| from_randomness | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 15 |\n| TOTAL_FEE_BPS (300) | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 5 |\n| calculate_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 12 |\n| split_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 17 |\n| TIER_AMOUNTS [6 tiers] | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 5 |\n| get_tier_amount | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 17 |\n| lifecycle::transition | lifecycle | shared/src/lifecycle.rs | — |\n| escrow (transfer helpers) | escrow | shared/src/escrow.rs | — |\n| timeout::is_expired | timeout | shared/src/timeout.rs | 12 |\n| pause::check_not_paused | pause | shared/src/pause.rs | 13 |\n| vrf_orao (read_orao_randomness, is_fulfilled) | vrf_orao | shared/src/vrf_orao.rs | 20 |\n| commit_reveal | commit_reveal | shared/src/commit_reveal.rs | — |\n| cpi (update_player_profile CPI) | cpi | shared/src/cpi.rs | — |\n\n### Game Engine Exports\n\n| Export | Package | File | Line |\n|--------|---------|------|------|\n| COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 10 |\n| getMatchPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 25 |\n| getConfigPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 36 |\n| getEntryAmount | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 48 |\n| calculatePotentialPayout | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 55 |\n| getOppositeSide | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 65 |\n| determineWinnerFromRandomness | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 72 |\n| CoinflipIDL / PlatformIDL | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 10 |\n| Coinflip / Platform types | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 6-7 |\n\n### Frontend Components\n\n| Component | File | Line |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| CoinflipProvider / useCoinflip | features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx | 69, 362 |\n| CoinSideSelector | features/coinflip/components/CoinSideSelector.tsx | 19 |\n| CoinAnimation | features/coinflip/components/CoinAnimation.tsx | 20 |\n| OpenMatchesList | features/coinflip/components/OpenMatchesList.tsx | 31 |\n| MatchCard | features/coinflip/components/MatchCard.tsx | 13 |\n| ActiveMatchView | features/coinflip/components/ActiveMatchView.tsx | 12 |\n| chain.ts (instruction builders + queries + claimable matches) | features/coinflip/utils/chain.ts | 187-310 |\n| verification.ts (verifyMatch + VerificationResult) | features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts | — |\n| helpers.ts (truncateAddress, getOppositeSide) | features/coinflip/utils/helpers.ts | 3, 7 |\n| CoinflipPage | pages/CoinflipPage.tsx | 450 |\n| FairnessPage (coinflip VRF verification section) | App.tsx | — |\n\n### Tests\n\n| Test | Type | File | Status |\n|------|------|------|--------|\n| initialize_config (1 test) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:360 | passing |\n| create_match (4 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:379-435 | passing |\n| join_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:461-513 | passing |\n| claim_payout (9 tests, incl. CPI) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:554-757 | passing |\n| cancel_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:793-827 | passing |\n| timeout_cancel (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:855-909 | passing |\n| full lifecycle (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:934-985 | passing |\n| platform program (5 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/platform.ts:97-203 | passing |\n| Frontend unit/component tests | vitest | — | none exist |\n| E2E tests | playwright | — | none exist |\n\n**Total: 31 bankrun tests passing (26 coinflip + 5 platform), 0 frontend tests, 0 E2E tests.**\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Audit\n\n### FR-1: Match Creation\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Player can select one of six tiers (Iron–Diamond) | SATISFIED | shared/src/tiers.rs:5 TIER_AMOUNTS, types.ts:25 TIER_AMOUNTS_LAMPORTS, CoinflipPage TierSelector |\n| 2 | Player can choose Heads or Tails | SATISFIED | shared/src/constants.rs:2-3 SIDE_HEADS/TAILS, CoinSideSelector.tsx:19 |\n| 3 | Created match appears in lobby with creator name, tier, amount, side | SATISFIED | MatchCard.tsx:13 (PlayerAvatar, tier, amount, side, join), chain.ts:139 fetchAllOpenMatches |\n| 4 | Match creation requires connected wallet with sufficient balance | SATISFIED | CoinflipContext.tsx:169 createMatch, error.rs:19 InsufficientFunds |\n| 5 | Only one active match per player (PDA constraint) | SATISFIED | state.rs:20 CoinflipMatch seeds [\"match\", creator], Anchor init constraint |\n\n### FR-2: Match Joining\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Browse open matches filtered by tier and sorted | SATISFIED | OpenMatchesList.tsx:43 tier filter, :18 sortMatches (newest/oldest/amount) |\n| 2 | Joining assigns the opposite side automatically | SATISFIED | join_match.rs:25, chain.ts:122-123 onChainMatchToUI |\n| 3 | Both players' wagers are equal (tier-enforced) | SATISFIED | create_match.rs:28 entry_amount from tier, join_match.rs:25 same amount |\n| 4 | Tier selection is locked once bet is placed | SATISFIED | state.rs:20 CoinflipMatch.tier immutable after creation |\n| 5 | Join requires connected wallet with sufficient balance | SATISFIED | CoinflipContext.tsx:206 joinMatch, chain.ts:241 buildJoinMatchTx |\n\n### FR-3: Flip Resolution\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Flip begins immediately when both players committed | SATISFIED | join_match embeds Orao VRF request CPI; frontend polls until randomness fulfilled. 3-tx flow: create→join(+VRF)→claim(+settle). |\n| 2 | VRF determines the outcome | SATISFIED | Orao VRF integrated via shared vrf_orao module. claim_payout reads Orao randomness account + derives winner via from_randomness. |\n| 3 | Result is deterministic and reproducible from VRF seed | SATISFIED | from_randomness(byte) is pure deterministic (shared/src/constants.rs:15). Orao randomness account persists on-chain. verification.ts re-derives result and confirms VRF fulfillment. |\n| 4 | Flip animation plays with coin rotation and landing | SATISFIED | CoinAnimation.tsx:20 CSS 3D transform with spinning-heads/spinning-tails classes, dual faces |\n\n### FR-4: Settlement and Payout\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Winner payout = total_pool × 0.97 (3% fee) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, fees.rs:5 TOTAL_FEE_BPS=300, test coinflip.ts:554 |\n| 2 | Platform fee collected to treasury PDA | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs treasury transfer, coinflip.ts:554 |\n| 3 | Payout eligibility recorded on-chain | SATISFIED | state.rs winner+claimed fields, claim_payout CPI to update_player_profile |\n| 4 | Winner can claim funds successfully | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, CoinflipContext.tsx:268, coinflip.ts:554 |\n| 5 | Either player can trigger settlement (loser not blocked) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs caller validated as creator OR opponent, payout always goes to winner |\n| 6 | Settlement is idempotent (no double-settle) | SATISFIED | error.rs AlreadyClaimed, coinflip.ts:666 \"rejects double claim (account closed)\" |\n| 7 | Replay protection for signed actions | SATISFIED | Match closed after claim (rent → creator), Anchor tx signature dedup |\n\n### FR-4b: Cancellation and Refunds\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Creator can cancel in WAITING phase | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs, phase==WAITING check |\n| 2 | Cancel refunds full entry amount + rent | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs close=creator, all lamports returned |\n| 3 | Timeout cancel refunds both players if VRF unresolved within 2 min | SATISFIED | timeout_cancel.rs, entry_amount refunded to each player, is_expired + !is_fulfilled guards |\n| 4 | No platform fee on cancellation | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs and timeout_cancel.rs have no fee calculation |\n| 5 | Either player can trigger timeout cancel | SATISFIED | timeout_cancel.rs caller == creator OR opponent |\n\n### FR-5: Fairness Verification\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Completed match displays VRF seed/proof details | SATISFIED | MatchSettled event emits randomness bytes + vrf_request_key (state.rs:63, claim_payout.rs:163). ActiveMatchView shows randomness hex, derived result, VRF fulfillment status after \"Verify Fairness\" click. |\n| 2 | Players can independently verify result matches VRF | SATISFIED | verification.ts:verifyMatch() re-derives result from Orao randomness via from_randomness(byte[0] % 2), compares to event winner, confirms Orao account fulfillment. |\n| 3 | Verification accessible from match history and result screen | SATISFIED | ActiveMatchView \"Verify Fairness\" button (post-claim). FairnessPage (/fairness) allows paste-a-tx-signature verification for any match. |\n\n### FR-6: Lobby Browser UI\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Open games list shows creator name/avatar, tier, amount, side, join button | SATISFIED | MatchCard.tsx:13 (PlayerAvatar:25, getDisplayName:28, tier:50, amount:41, side:36, join:57) |\n| 2 | Filter by tier | SATISFIED | OpenMatchesList.tsx:43 `matches.filter(m => m.tier === selectedTier)` |\n| 3 | Sort by newest/oldest/amount | SATISFIED | OpenMatchesList.tsx:18 sortMatches, :79 select dropdown |\n| 4 | Create Game panel with tier selection grid and Heads/Tails toggle | SATISFIED | CoinflipPage.tsx sidebar: TierSelector + CoinSideSelector.tsx:19 |\n| 5 | Estimated wait time (deferred if data unavailable) | DEFERRED | Self-deferred in criterion text (\"deferred to post-MVP polish if data unavailable\"). Requires match fill-rate analytics infrastructure. |\n\n### FR-7: Active Game and Result UI\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Both players shown with avatars, names, wager amounts | SATISFIED | ActiveMatchView.tsx:88-108 PlayerAvatarCompact, side labels, entry amount |\n| 2 | 3D coin flip animation with multiple rotations and gradual slowdown | SATISFIED | CoinAnimation.tsx:20 CSS 3D transform (front/back faces :53-58), spinning classes :43-45 |\n| 3 | Winning side highlighted with glow effect | SATISFIED | ActiveMatchView.tsx:200-205 result color + textShadow glow |\n| 4 | \"YOU WIN!\" or \"YOU LOSE\" overlay displayed | SATISFIED | ActiveMatchView.tsx:128 \"You Won!\", :129-139 \"You Lost\" with heart+shards animation |\n| 5 | Payout amount shown for winner | SATISFIED | ActiveMatchView.tsx:207-210 `match.payoutAmount.toFixed(4) SOL` |\n| 6 | Quick rematch option available after result | SATISFIED | \"Play Again\" button in ActiveMatchView post-claim section. Calls createMatch with same tier/side. Opponent must find and join from lobby. |\n\n### FR-8: Audio Feedback\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Coin flip spinning sound during animation | DEFERRED | Scope Decisions: \"Deferred to later spec: Audio integration...\" |\n| 2 | Dramatic pause before landing | DEFERRED | Same reference. |\n| 3 | Victory sound for winner | DEFERRED | Same reference. |\n| 4 | Coin clink on landing | DEFERRED | Same reference. |\n\n## Gap Summary\n\n| # | FR | Criterion | Severity | Category | Blocked By | Next Step |\n|---|-----|-----------|----------|----------|------------|-----------|\n| — | — | — | — | — | — | **All implementation gaps resolved.** Only deferred items remain. |\n\n## Resolved Items\n\n| Item | Resolution | Date |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| VRF oracle/resolver (FR-3.1, FR-3.2) | Orao VRF integrated via shared vrf_orao module. join_match embeds VRF request CPI; claim_payout reads randomness at claim time. 3-tx flow: create→join(+VRF)→claim(+settle). Previous MagicBlock VRF and resolve_match instruction deleted in 004 rewrite. | 2026-02-26 |\n| VRF reproducibility (FR-3.3) | from_randomness(byte) is pure deterministic (constants.rs:15). verification.ts re-derives result from Orao randomness bytes. Orao randomness account persists on-chain for proof. | 2026-02-26 |\n| VRF seed/proof display (FR-5.1) | MatchSettled event emits randomness bytes + vrf_request_key. ActiveMatchView displays verification details after \"Verify Fairness\" click. | 2026-02-26 |\n| Independent verification (FR-5.2) | verification.ts:verifyMatch() fetches tx, extracts MatchSettled event, re-derives result, confirms Orao account fulfillment. | 2026-02-26 |\n| Verification accessibility (FR-5.3) | \"Verify Fairness\" button in ActiveMatchView (post-claim). FairnessPage (/fairness) supports paste-a-tx-signature verification. | 2026-02-26 |\n| Quick rematch (FR-7.6) | \"Play Again\" button in ActiveMatchView. Creates new open match with same tier/side via existing createMatch action. | 2026-02-26 |\n| Timeout safety net | timeout_cancel instruction: either player can cancel LOCKED match after 2 min timeout if VRF unfulfilled. Refunds both players. Uses shared::timeout::is_expired + shared::vrf_orao::is_fulfilled guards. | 2026-02-19 |\n| Claimable matches | fetchClaimableMatches() in chain.ts with dual memcmp queries (creator/opponent). \"Your Matches\" section in CoinflipPage with claim/cancel/view actions. | 2026-02-26 |\n\n## Deferred Items\n\n| Item | Deferred To | Target Spec | Target Status | Stale? |\n|------|-------------|-------------|---------------|--------|\n| Estimated wait time (FR-6.5) | post-MVP polish | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |\n| Spinning sound (FR-8.1) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n| Dramatic pause sound (FR-8.2) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n| Victory sound (FR-8.3) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n| Coin clink sound (FR-8.4) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |\n\n5 deferred items remain. All FR-5 and FR-7.6 items previously deferred are now **RESOLVED**.\n\n## Recommendations\n\n1. **Audio spec**: All 4 FR-8 items should be bundled into a dedicated audio/SFX spec covering sound design across all games. Low priority for launch.\n\n2. **Estimated wait time (FR-6.5)**: Self-deferred and low priority. Requires match fill-rate analytics data that doesn't exist yet. Safe to keep deferred past launch.\n\n3. **Frontend test coverage**: Zero vitest/component tests and zero Playwright E2E tests exist. Not an FR criterion but notable for launch readiness. Consider adding to E2E integration spec (203).\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":298,"cache_read_input_tokens":64863,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":298},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a3554eb9-5d3e-4470-b8e4-3c2e723bd989","uuid":"de1c0533-9d95-4749-a836-602f328d024a"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XTJXzzdgqqQs9ofoUipq4C","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/gap-analysis.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a3554eb9-5d3e-4470-b8e4-3c2e723bd989","uuid":"57e1733f-387d-4b6a-96e8-13aefdbfccd6","tool_use_result":{"type":"update","filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/gap-analysis.md","content":"# Gap Analysis: 001-coinflip — Coinflip\n\n- **Date**: 2026-02-26\n- **Spec status**: Done\n- **Previous analysis**: 2026-02-18 (pre-004 rewrite)\n\n## Implementation Inventory\n\n### On-Chain Instructions\n\n| Instruction | Program | File | Line |\n|------------|---------|------|------|\n| initialize_config | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/initialize_config.rs | 24 |\n| create_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/create_match.rs | 28 |\n| join_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/join_match.rs | 25 |\n| claim_payout | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs | 55 |\n| cancel_match | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/cancel_match.rs | 24 |\n| timeout_cancel | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/timeout_cancel.rs | 32 |\n| force_close | coinflip | programs/coinflip/src/instructions/force_close.rs | — |\n| initialize_platform | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/initialize_platform.rs | 25 |\n| create_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/create_player_profile.rs | 24 |\n| update_player_profile | platform | programs/platform/src/instructions/update_player_profile.rs | 20 |\n\n**Architecture**: 3-tx flow — create → join(+Orao VRF request) → claim(+VRF read + settle). The previous `resolve_match` instruction was deleted in the 004 shared-infrastructure rewrite; resolution is now handled at claim time by reading Orao VRF randomness on-chain.\n\n### Shared Crate\n\n| Export | Module | File | Line |\n|--------|--------|------|------|\n| SIDE_HEADS / SIDE_TAILS | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 2-3 |\n| PHASE_WAITING / LOCKED / SETTLED / CANCELLED | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 6-9 |\n| LOCK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS (120) | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 12 |\n| from_randomness | constants | shared/src/constants.rs | 15 |\n| TOTAL_FEE_BPS (300) | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 5 |\n| calculate_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 12 |\n| split_fee | fees | shared/src/fees.rs | 17 |\n| TIER_AMOUNTS [6 tiers] | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 5 |\n| get_tier_amount | tiers | shared/src/tiers.rs | 17 |\n| lifecycle::transition | lifecycle | shared/src/lifecycle.rs | — |\n| escrow (transfer helpers) | escrow | shared/src/escrow.rs | — |\n| timeout::is_expired | timeout | shared/src/timeout.rs | 12 |\n| pause::check_not_paused | pause | shared/src/pause.rs | 13 |\n| vrf_orao (read_orao_randomness, is_fulfilled) | vrf_orao | shared/src/vrf_orao.rs | 20 |\n| commit_reveal | commit_reveal | shared/src/commit_reveal.rs | — |\n| cpi (update_player_profile CPI) | cpi | shared/src/cpi.rs | — |\n\n### Game Engine Exports\n\n| Export | Package | File | Line |\n|--------|---------|------|------|\n| COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 10 |\n| getMatchPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 25 |\n| getConfigPda | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 36 |\n| getEntryAmount | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 48 |\n| calculatePotentialPayout | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 55 |\n| getOppositeSide | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 65 |\n| determineWinnerFromRandomness | game-engine | packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts | 72 |\n| CoinflipIDL / PlatformIDL | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 10 |\n| Coinflip / Platform types | anchor-client | packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts | 6-7 |\n\n### Frontend Components\n\n| Component | File | Line |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| CoinflipProvider / useCoinflip | features/coinflip/context/CoinflipContext.tsx | 69, 362 |\n| CoinSideSelector | features/coinflip/components/CoinSideSelector.tsx | 19 |\n| CoinAnimation | features/coinflip/components/CoinAnimation.tsx | 20 |\n| OpenMatchesList | features/coinflip/components/OpenMatchesList.tsx | 31 |\n| MatchCard | features/coinflip/components/MatchCard.tsx | 13 |\n| ActiveMatchView | features/coinflip/components/ActiveMatchView.tsx | 12 |\n| chain.ts (instruction builders + queries + claimable matches) | features/coinflip/utils/chain.ts | 187-310 |\n| verification.ts (verifyMatch + VerificationResult) | features/coinflip/utils/verification.ts | — |\n| helpers.ts (truncateAddress, getOppositeSide) | features/coinflip/utils/helpers.ts | 3, 7 |\n| CoinflipPage | pages/CoinflipPage.tsx | 450 |\n| FairnessPage (coinflip VRF verification section) | App.tsx | — |\n\n### Tests\n\n| Test | Type | File | Status |\n|------|------|------|--------|\n| initialize_config (1 test) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:360 | passing |\n| create_match (4 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:379-435 | passing |\n| join_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:461-513 | passing |\n| claim_payout (9 tests, incl. CPI) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:554-757 | passing |\n| cancel_match (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:793-827 | passing |\n| timeout_cancel (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:855-909 | passing |\n| full lifecycle (3 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/coinflip.ts:934-985 | passing |\n| platform program (5 tests) | bankrun | solana/tests/platform.ts:97-203 | passing |\n| Frontend unit/component tests | vitest | — | none exist |\n| E2E tests | playwright | — | none exist |\n\n**Total: 31 bankrun tests passing (26 coinflip + 5 platform), 0 frontend tests, 0 E2E tests.**\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Audit\n\n### FR-1: Match Creation\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Player can select one of six tiers (Iron–Diamond) | SATISFIED | shared/src/tiers.rs:5 TIER_AMOUNTS, types.ts:25 TIER_AMOUNTS_LAMPORTS, CoinflipPage TierSelector |\n| 2 | Player can choose Heads or Tails | SATISFIED | shared/src/constants.rs:2-3 SIDE_HEADS/TAILS, CoinSideSelector.tsx:19 |\n| 3 | Created match appears in lobby with creator name, tier, amount, side | SATISFIED | MatchCard.tsx:13 (PlayerAvatar, tier, amount, side, join), chain.ts:139 fetchAllOpenMatches |\n| 4 | Match creation requires connected wallet with sufficient balance | SATISFIED | CoinflipContext.tsx:169 createMatch, error.rs:19 InsufficientFunds |\n| 5 | Only one active match per player (PDA constraint) | SATISFIED | state.rs:20 CoinflipMatch seeds [\"match\", creator], Anchor init constraint |\n\n### FR-2: Match Joining\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Browse open matches filtered by tier and sorted | SATISFIED | OpenMatchesList.tsx:43 tier filter, :18 sortMatches (newest/oldest/amount) |\n| 2 | Joining assigns the opposite side automatically | SATISFIED | join_match.rs:25, chain.ts:122-123 onChainMatchToUI |\n| 3 | Both players' wagers are equal (tier-enforced) | SATISFIED | create_match.rs:28 entry_amount from tier, join_match.rs:25 same amount |\n| 4 | Tier selection is locked once bet is placed | SATISFIED | state.rs:20 CoinflipMatch.tier immutable after creation |\n| 5 | Join requires connected wallet with sufficient balance | SATISFIED | CoinflipContext.tsx:206 joinMatch, chain.ts:241 buildJoinMatchTx |\n\n### FR-3: Flip Resolution\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Flip begins immediately when both players committed | SATISFIED | join_match embeds Orao VRF request CPI; frontend polls until randomness fulfilled. 3-tx flow: create→join(+VRF)→claim(+settle). |\n| 2 | VRF determines the outcome | SATISFIED | Orao VRF integrated via shared vrf_orao module. claim_payout reads Orao randomness account + derives winner via from_randomness. |\n| 3 | Result is deterministic and reproducible from VRF seed | SATISFIED | from_randomness(byte) is pure deterministic (shared/src/constants.rs:15). Orao randomness account persists on-chain. verification.ts re-derives result and confirms VRF fulfillment. |\n| 4 | Flip animation plays with coin rotation and landing | SATISFIED | CoinAnimation.tsx:20 CSS 3D transform with spinning-heads/spinning-tails classes, dual faces |\n\n### FR-4: Settlement and Payout\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Winner payout = total_pool × 0.97 (3% fee) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, fees.rs:5 TOTAL_FEE_BPS=300, test coinflip.ts:554 |\n| 2 | Platform fee collected to treasury PDA | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs treasury transfer, coinflip.ts:554 |\n| 3 | Payout eligibility recorded on-chain | SATISFIED | state.rs winner+claimed fields, claim_payout CPI to update_player_profile |\n| 4 | Winner can claim funds successfully | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, CoinflipContext.tsx:268, coinflip.ts:554 |\n| 5 | Either player can trigger settlement (loser not blocked) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs caller validated as creator OR opponent, payout always goes to winner |\n| 6 | Settlement is idempotent (no double-settle) | SATISFIED | error.rs AlreadyClaimed, coinflip.ts:666 \"rejects double claim (account closed)\" |\n| 7 | Replay protection for signed actions | SATISFIED | Match closed after claim (rent → creator), Anchor tx signature dedup |\n\n### FR-4b: Cancellation and Refunds\n\n| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |\n|---|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | Creator can cancel in WAITING phase | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs, phase==WAITING check |\n| 2 | Cancel refunds full entry amount + rent | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs close=creator, all lamports returned |\n| 3 | Timeout cancel refunds both players if