"," | # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |"," |---|-----------|--------|----------|","-| 1 | Flip begins immediately when both players committed | RESOLVED | MagicBlock Ephemeral VRF callback now active on devnet. join_match CPIs into VRF program which calls back resolve_match. Program redeployed without mock-oracle feature (2026-02-19). |","-| 2 | VRF determines the outcome | RESOLVED | MagicBlock Ephemeral VRF integrated. join_match.rs:88-123 sends VRF request, VRF program calls back resolve_match with randomness. Oracle authority = PDA([\"identity\"], VRF_PROGRAM). |","-| 3 | Result is deterministic and reproducible from VRF seed | PARTIAL | from_randomness(byte) is deterministic. VRF proof exists on-chain via MagicBlock but no UI to display/verify it yet. |","+| 1 | Flip begins immediately when both players committed | SATISFIED | join_match embeds Orao VRF request CPI; frontend polls until randomness fulfilled. 3-tx flow: create→join(+VRF)→claim(+settle). |","+| 2 | VRF determines the outcome | SATISFIED | Orao VRF integrated via shared vrf_orao module. claim_payout reads Orao randomness account + derives winner via from_randomness. |","+| 3 | Result is deterministic and reproducible from VRF seed | SATISFIED | from_randomness(byte) is pure deterministic (shared/src/constants.rs:15). Orao randomness account persists on-chain. verification.ts re-derives result and confirms VRF fulfillment. |"," | 4 | Flip animation plays with coin rotation and landing | SATISFIED | CoinAnimation.tsx:20 CSS 3D transform with spinning-heads/spinning-tails classes, dual faces |"," "," ### FR-4: Settlement and Payout"," "," | # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |"," |---|-----------|--------|----------|","-| 1 | Winner payout = total_pool × 0.97 (3% fee) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, fees.rs:5 TOTAL_FEE_BPS=300, test coinflip.ts:575 |","-| 2 | Platform fee collected to treasury PDA | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs treasury transfer, coinflip.ts:575 |","+| 1 | Winner payout = total_pool × 0.97 (3% fee) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, fees.rs:5 TOTAL_FEE_BPS=300, test coinflip.ts:554 |","+| 2 | Platform fee collected to treasury PDA | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs treasury transfer, coinflip.ts:554 |"," | 3 | Payout eligibility recorded on-chain | SATISFIED | state.rs winner+claimed fields, claim_payout CPI to update_player_profile |","-| 4 | Winner can claim funds successfully | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, CoinflipContext.tsx:268, coinflip.ts:575 |","-| 5 | Settlement is idempotent (no double-settle) | SATISFIED | error.rs AlreadyClaimed, coinflip.ts:617 \"rejects double claim\" |","-| 6 | Replay protection for signed actions | SATISFIED | Match closed after claim (rent → creator), Anchor tx signature dedup |","+| 4 | Winner can claim funds successfully | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs:55, CoinflipContext.tsx:268, coinflip.ts:554 |","+| 5 | Either player can trigger settlement (loser not blocked) | SATISFIED | claim_payout.rs caller validated as creator OR opponent, payout always goes to winner |","+| 6 | Settlement is idempotent (no double-settle) | SATISFIED | error.rs AlreadyClaimed, coinflip.ts:666 \"rejects double claim (account closed)\" |","+| 7 | Replay protection for signed actions | SATISFIED | Match closed after claim (rent → creator), Anchor tx signature dedup |"," ","+### FR-4b: Cancellation and Refunds","+","+| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |","+|---|-----------|--------|----------|","+| 1 | Creator can cancel in WAITING phase | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs, phase==WAITING check |","+| 2 | Cancel refunds full entry amount + rent | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs close=creator, all lamports returned |","+| 3 | Timeout cancel refunds both players if VRF unresolved within 2 min | SATISFIED | timeout_cancel.rs, entry_amount refunded to each player, is_expired + !is_fulfilled guards |","+| 4 | No platform fee on cancellation | SATISFIED | cancel_match.rs and timeout_cancel.rs have no fee calculation |","+| 5 | Either player can trigger timeout cancel | SATISFIED | timeout_cancel.rs caller == creator OR opponent |","+"," ### FR-5: Fairness Verification"," "," | # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |"," |---|-----------|--------|----------|","-| 1 | Completed match displays VRF seed/proof details | DEFERRED | UI fields exist in CoinflipPage but chain.ts:133 sets seedHash=\"\" and no VRF proof populated. Deferred (Scope Decisions: \"fairness verification UI\"). |","-| 2 | Players can independently verify result matches VRF | DEFERRED | VRF integration deferred (Scope Decisions). |","-| 3 | Verification accessible from match history and result screen | DEFERRED | CoinflipPage has /fairness link in history modal but no verification logic. Deferred (Scope Decisions). |","+| 1 | Completed match displays VRF seed/proof details | SATISFIED | MatchSettled event emits randomness bytes + vrf_request_key (state.rs:63, claim_payout.rs:163). ActiveMatchView shows randomness hex, derived result, VRF fulfillment status after \"Verify Fairness\" click. |","+| 2 | Players can independently verify result matches VRF | SATISFIED | verification.ts:verifyMatch() re-derives result from Orao randomness via from_randomness(byte[0] % 2), compares to event winner, confirms Orao account fulfillment. |","+| 3 | Verification accessible from match history and result screen | SATISFIED | ActiveMatchView \"Verify Fairness\" button (post-claim). FairnessPage (/fairness) allows paste-a-tx-signature verification for any match. |"," "," ### FR-6: Lobby Browser UI"," "]},{"oldStart":138,"oldLines":7,"newStart":160,"newLines":7,"lines":[" | 2 | Filter by tier | SATISFIED | OpenMatchesList.tsx:43 `matches.filter(m => m.tier === selectedTier)` |"," | 3 | Sort by newest/oldest/amount | SATISFIED | OpenMatchesList.tsx:18 sortMatches, :79 select dropdown |"," | 4 | Create Game panel with tier selection grid and Heads/Tails toggle | SATISFIED | CoinflipPage.tsx sidebar: TierSelector + CoinSideSelector.tsx:19 |","-| 5 | Estimated wait time (deferr