eout_cancel instruction: either player can cancel LOCKED match after 2 min timeout if VRF unfulfilled. Refunds both players. Uses shared::timeout::is_expired + shared::vrf_orao::is_fulfilled guards. | 2026-02-19 |","+| Claimable matches | fetchClaimableMatches() in chain.ts with dual memcmp queries (creator/opponent). \"Your Matches\" section in CoinflipPage with claim/cancel/view actions. | 2026-02-26 |"," "," ## Deferred Items"," "," | Item | Deferred To | Target Spec | Target Status | Stale? |"," |------|-------------|-------------|---------------|--------|","-| VRF reproducibility (FR-3.3) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","-| VRF seed/proof display (FR-5.1) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","-| Independent verification (FR-5.2) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","-| Verification accessibility (FR-5.3) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |"," | Estimated wait time (FR-6.5) | post-MVP polish | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","-| Spinning sound (FR-8.1) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","-| Dramatic pause sound (FR-8.2) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","-| Victory sound (FR-8.3) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","-| Coin clink sound (FR-8.4) | later spec | none specified | — | UNTRACKED |","+| Spinning sound (FR-8.1) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |","+| Dramatic pause sound (FR-8.2) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |","+| Victory sound (FR-8.3) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |","+| Coin clink sound (FR-8.4) | later spec | dedicated audio spec | — | UNTRACKED |"," ","-All 10 deferred items are **UNTRACKED** — none reference a specific target spec. All other specs (002-crash through 105-tug-of-earn) remain in Draft status.","+5 deferred items remain. All FR-5 and FR-7.6 items previously deferred are now **RESOLVED**."," "," ## Recommendations"," ","-1. ~~**Critical gap — Oracle/resolver service**~~: **RES